				<h1>Andreas Antonopoulos Starts Fundraiser For Dorian Nakamoto, Man Pegged as Bitcoin Creator</h1>
		
	<div class="author">
		<span class="hover-effect left">
			<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0a42e736f06a818d06d5fd81e3f25575?s=50&d=http://newsbtc.com/wp-content/themes/allegro-theme/images/_avatar-50x50.jpg&r=G" alt="Eric Calouro" />
		</span>
		<div class="a-content">
			<span>By <b>Eric Calouro</b></span>
			<span class="meta">
				March 7, 2014 13:03							</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	</div>

</div>				
