				<div class="content-block main left">
				<div class="block">
											<div class="post-3302 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-news category-online tag-andreasantonopoulos tag-dorian tag-fundraiser block-content">
								<p>
		<span class="hover-effect">
			<img class="image-border" src="http://newsbtc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Andreas-Dorian-Tweet-890x395.jpg" alt="Andreas Antonopoulos Starts Fundraiser For Dorian Nakamoto, Man Pegged as Bitcoin Creator" />		</span>
	</p>
							<div class="shortcode-content">
								<div class="paragraph-row">
																			<div class="column3">
																							
	<h3 class="highlight-title">Related Articles</h3>
	<ul>
