									<a href="http://newsbtc.com/2014/06/15/holiday-inn-location-in-new-york-to-accept-bitcoin-payments-pilot/#comments" class="h-comment"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="6507 http://newsbtc.com/?p=6507">0</span></a>
					<span class="meta-date">15.Jun</span>
